body_html: Just to note, it's actually already set to save preview bitmaps (but probably shouldn't be). This means that currently you don't need to do anything other than "adb pull /sdcard/data/data/saved_images/preview.png" to grab the latest classified preview image.

body: Just to note, it's actually already set to save preview bitmaps (but probably shouldn't be). This means that currently you don't need to do anything other than "adb pull /sdcard/data/data/saved_images/preview.png" to grab the latest classified preview image.
